name: Happy?
description:
"Happy?" - By Bryant W

"In this hole that is me
A life that's growing feeble
In this hole so limiting
The sun has set, all darkens" -Mudvayne

Enjoy the future!

This artwork was created using old public domain illustrations collage together and remixed with patterns and other effects in Photoshop.
